                                    <div class=3D"column column-6082-0 has-=
fill">


            <div class=3D"asset asset-text asset-force-padding">
                <p style=3D"text-align: center;">The Mohs Hardness Scale is=
 non-linear and therefore does not provide a true reflection of the relatio=
nship between the hardnesses&nbsp;featured in the scale. There are many oth=
er hardness tools available but the Mohs Scale has been widely used across =
the world due to how easy and inexpensive it is.</p>
            </div>
